===========

This analysis shows that while Zimbabwe has reported a significant decline among both men and women, there are important differentials that suggest that the epidemic in Zimbabwe is heterogeneous and warrants closer examination of these variations. The changes in HIV prevalence were more pronounced in some provincial regions, among young women and is associated with adoption of safer sexual behaviours. Disclaimer {#sec018}
